  "1425980": {
    "name": "Stone Simulator – Just Be a Rock",
    "steam_appid": 1425980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为一块石头/岩石/巨石。什么也不做，只需存在。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松、冥想，静观季节在最宁静的模拟器中更迭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/b02e78591c0e43806274082eb2c1713c.poster.avif?t=1765573204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/b02e78591c0e43806274082eb2c1713c.webm?t=1765573204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/b02e78591c0e43806274082eb2c1713c.mp4?t=1765573204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾经想过成为一块岩石是什么感觉吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个宁静且不断变化的世界中，成为一块坚定不移的石头。经历数百年的季节、更迭的天气以及荒诞而平凡的冒险。长出青苔、收集鸟粪，并质疑你的存在——《石头模拟器》既是你从未意识到自己需要的禅修冥想，也可能是史上最无聊的游戏。由你来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《石头模拟器》是一段奇趣而冥想的体验，让你拥抱作为一块真正石头那激动人心的生活。静观世界在几十年、数年乃至数个世纪中悄然流逝，季节轮转，自然（或混沌）在你周围展开。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏亮点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌦️ 季节与天气：在暴风雪、夏日热浪、秋雨和春雨中求生。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕰️ 时光飞逝：观看日子、岁月和世纪的流逝</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 荒诞成就：解锁“存在危机”（连续三年无所作为）等足以成为梗的奖杯，以及更多其他成就。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/6687cb9107b1095d49c9cbfef8872c13.poster.avif?t=1765573204\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/6687cb9107b1095d49c9cbfef8872c13.webm?t=1765573204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1425980/extras/6687cb9107b1095d49c9cbfef8872c13.mp4?t=1765573204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >为什么要做一块石头？</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >禅模式：在宁静的环境音和极简视觉中放松身心。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梗燃料：完美适合追求讽刺的主播或喜欢“烂到极致”幽默的玩家。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >零操作要求：你唯一的任务？只需存在。（说真的，你甚至无法移动。）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
